  "work": {
    "selected": [
      {
        "id": "cdp-portal",
        "img": "assets/work/CDP Developer Portal/portal-dashboard.png",
        "tag": "Product · 0→1",
        "title": "CDP Developer Portal",
        "description": "Led product for an all-new logged-in developer platform (dashboard, wallets, onramp, and API key management) built to get developers from signup to first integration in minutes.",
        "link": "https://www.coinbase.com/developer-platform",
        "linkLabel": "cdp.coinbase.com ↗",
        "role": "Product Manager",
        "year": "2023-2024",
        "company": "Coinbase Developer Platform",
        "body": [
          "The Coinbase Developer Platform (CDP) needed a logged-in home: somewhere developers could manage their projects, spin up wallets, configure onramp flows, and rotate API keys without digging through docs or emailing support.",
          "I led product for the 0→1 build of that portal: defining scope, writing specs, running design reviews, and coordinating across engineering, design, and legal to ship the first version. The goal was simple: get a developer from signup to their first successful API call in under five minutes.",
          "The portal launched with dashboard, wallet management, onramp configuration, and API key management. Post-launch, we iterated on the onboarding funnel based on activation data and cut time-to-first-call by roughly 40%."
        ],
        "images": [
          "assets/work/CDP Developer Portal/portal-welcome.mp4",
          "assets/work/CDP Developer Portal/portal-dashboard.png",
          "assets/work/CDP Developer Portal/portal-api-keys.mp4",
          "assets/work/CDP Developer Portal/portal-payments.mp4",
          "assets/work/CDP Developer Portal/portal-customer-resources.mp4"
        ],
        "heroVideo": "assets/work/CDP Developer Portal/portal-welcome.mp4"
      },
      {
        "id": "cdp-docs",
        "img": "assets/work/cdp-docs/cdp-docs-preview.jpg",
        "tag": "Docs · AI",
        "title": "AI-Native Docs, with Mintlify",
        "description": "Led a full overhaul of CDP's developer docs: rebuilt the information architecture, shipped AI-first features like one-click copy-to-LLM and an MCP server, and cut internal preview build times from 30 minutes to under one. Shipped in 6 weeks.",
        "link": "https://www.coinbase.com/blog/coinbase-pm-blog-ai-docs-and-mintlify",
        "linkLabel": "Read my writeup on Coinbase's blog ↗",
        "role": "Product Manager",
        "year": "2024",
        "company": "Coinbase Developer Platform",
        "body": [
          "CDP's developer docs had grown organically for years: inconsistent information architecture, a slow internal preview loop, and no affordances for how developers actually use docs now (copy-pasting into LLMs, asking AI assistants directly).",
          "I scoped a full overhaul in partnership with Mintlify: rebuilt the IA from scratch, consolidated hundreds of pages, and shipped a set of AI-native features: one-click copy-to-LLM for any code block, an MCP server so developers could query the docs from their AI tools, and better search. On the tooling side, we cut internal preview build times from 30 minutes to under one, so the docs team could actually iterate in real time.",
          "Shipped in 6 weeks. I wrote up the full story (the ETH Denver research that kicked this off, what we learned, what I'd do differently) on Coinbase's blog, linked above."
        ],
        "images": [],
        "heroVideo": "assets/work/cdp-docs/cdp-docs-preview.mp4",
        "linkDirect": true
      }
    ],
